{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/creative/brain-hole/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"fa5cef09-87ca-5750-b903-8eaf0dfdeb49","excerpt":"这个公众号是我的脑洞集散地。有时候我会突发奇想要做一些东西，可能是一个小网页，一个小程序，或者是一个小装置，我就会在这里把它们记录下来。目前写了 5 篇： 不就是找对象嘛，我一分钟能找 10…","html":"<p>这个公众号是我的脑洞集散地。有时候我会突发奇想要做一些东西，可能是一个小网页，一个小程序，或者是一个小装置，我就会在这里把它们记录下来。目前写了 5 篇：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Qoap_L88CF9GhX6GSCyoWg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">不就是找对象嘛，我一分钟能找 100 个</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/bm3TsZsoQKXNG2F32lhJ3Q\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">朋友圈不值得</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/z1TXWAk49dubJh16ExHKUw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">程序员结婚真可怕</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7RPqe668iOXF50sgJytmtA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">折叠屏膜难贴</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/4bDnU9PZWBMQ_doAC28ZcQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">要给每个程序员做一件独一无二的格子衬衣</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>最近，<strong>我在这里做一个「每日脑洞」的实验</strong>——每天会发一张自己的脑洞图，可能是一幅画，也可能是一张 ps 过的照片。</p>\n<p>一下摘录几张我比较喜欢的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>#2 我可以吃一小口井盖儿吗？</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/5caea/jinggai.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 125.62499999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jinggai\"\n        title=\"jinggai\"\n        src=\"/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/6af66/jinggai.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/69538/jinggai.png 160w,\n/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/72799/jinggai.png 320w,\n/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/6af66/jinggai.png 640w,\n/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/d9199/jinggai.png 960w,\n/static/d339065ea1cafacd09764c795ef6f872/5caea/jinggai.png 996w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>#6 每天早上起来第一件事就是打开窗。</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/3fca6/open-window.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 123.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"open window\"\n        title=\"open window\"\n        src=\"/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/6af66/open-window.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/69538/open-window.png 160w,\n/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/72799/open-window.png 320w,\n/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/6af66/open-window.png 640w,\n/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/d9199/open-window.png 960w,\n/static/f6d99893704ed7fb152fce02786bb06e/3fca6/open-window.png 1112w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:abso